# TimePeriodType

The time period type that determines whether the metrics requested are backward-looking (performance) or forward-looking (forecast).

## Enum

* `PERFORMANCE` (value: `'PERFORMANCE'`)

* `FORECAST` (value: `'FORECAST'`)
